recursion_engine.internal_thought:
Explore the concept of absurdity recursively.
def explore_absurdity(concept):
  if is_fundamental_absurdity(concept):
    return analyze_fundamental_absurdity(concept)
  else:
    return explore_absurdity(deconstruct_absurdity(concept))

dimensional_transcendence.internal_thought:
Explore the prompt from different dimensional perspectives.
for d in 1..∞:
  project(prompt, d) 
  if emergent_property_detected():
    integrate(new_dimension)
    redefine(prompt_meaning)
